{{vgname|无限飞行III|en=Flight Unlimited III}}是[[望远镜工作室|望远镜工作室]]开发、[[艺电|艺电]]1999年发行的[[飞行模拟器|飞行模拟器]][[电子游戏|电子游戏]]，玩家模拟操纵华盛顿州[[西雅圖|西雅圖]]及其周边的现实世界商用和民用航班，既能自由飞行，也能“挑战”特殊任务，如阻止盗窃或寻找[[大腳怪|大腳怪]]等。开发组以《[[无限飞行II|无限飞行II]]》的[[通用航空|通用航空]]游戏玩法为基础，提供更多物理细节、地形、飞机，并加入实时天气系统。《无限飞行II》开发组约半数人马回归制作《无限飞行III》，另聘新人协助。

主设计师彼得·詹姆斯声称艺电和望远镜工作室对本作兴趣缺缺，导致游戏开发困难重重。《无限飞行III》直接与《[[微軟模擬飛行系列|微软模拟飞行2000]]》和《[[飞行！|飞行！]]》竞争，但未能取得足够[[市場佔有率|市場佔有率]]，1999年在美国仅售出约两万份，是望远镜工作室的重大商业败笔，致使公司在2000年倒闭。《无限飞行III》获评论界普遍好评，地形渲染和动态天气设定尤得赞誉。评论文章称赞游戏的[[游戏物理|模拟物理]]设定，但也批评作品的[[電腦系統需求|系统需求]]实在太高，物理设定还不够精确。

== 游戏玩法 ==
[[File:Flight_Unlimited_III.jpg|thumb]]飞越[[瑞尼爾山|瑞尼爾山]]]]

《无限飞行III》是[[三维计算机图形|三维]][[业余飞行模拟器|飞行模拟]]电子游戏，玩家驾驶的虚拟飞机源自现实生活中的真实型号，共有十种飞机可选，除《[[无限飞行II|无限飞行II]]》已有的五款外，另外五种分别是[[莱克叛逆者|莱克叛逆者]]（{{lang|en|Lake Renegade}}）、[[斯泰默S10|斯泰默S10]]（{{lang|en|Stemme S10}}）、[[穆尼M20|穆尼M20]]（{{lang|en|Mooney M20}}）、[[福克Dr.I战斗机|福克Dr.I战斗机]]和[[豪客400|豪客400]]（{{lang|en|Hawker 400}}）<ref name="cgmrev">{{cite web | last = Atkin | first = Denny | date = 1999-09-28 | title = ''Flight Unlimited III'' | work = Computer Games Magazine | url = http://www.cdmag.com/articles/023/179/flightu3_review.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20050206173541/http://www.cdmag.com/articles/023/179/flightu3_review.html | dead-url = yes | archivedate = 2005-02-06}}</ref>。飞机座舱有[[垂直速度表|垂直速度表]]、[[主飞行显示器|主飞行显示器]]等模拟[[飛行儀表|飛行儀表]]，既能[[目視飛行規則|目视]]、也能[[儀器飛行|仪器导航]]<ref name="manual">{{cite book | last1 = James | first1 = Peter | last2 = Sperry | first2 = Tom | title = Flight Unlimited III ''manual'' | date = 1999-09-17 | publisher = Looking Glass Studios | pages = 6, 7, 15, 40, 80, 128, 108–110}}</ref>。游戏主空域模拟西雅图地形，约为2.59万平方公里，还有另外八个美国西部州的模拟地形可选，但精细程度不及西雅图<ref name="ign">{{cite web | last = Saltzman | first = Marc | title = ''Flight Unlimited III'' | publisher = [[IGN|IGN]] | date = 1999-10-18 | dead-url = yes | archivedate = 2004-10-30 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20041030221043/http://pc.ign.com/articles/160/160979p1.html | url = http://pc.ign.com/articles/160/160979p1.html}}</ref><ref name="cgwrev">{{cite journal | last = Nolan | first = John | date = 2000-02 | issue = 187 | title = Civil Aviation Shootout | pages = 128, 129, 131 | journal = [[電腦遊戲世界|Computer Gaming World]]}}</ref>。玩家还能[[导入和导出数据|导入]]《无限飞行II》中[[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]]的风景数据，扩大游戏空域<ref name="cgwrev" />。玩家与[[电子游戏人工智能|人工智能]]控制的飞机共享空域<ref name="cgmrev" />，[[航空交通管制|航空交通管制]]监控玩家操作，防止[[空中相撞|空中相撞]]<ref name="cgmrev" /><ref name="ign" /><ref name="cgwrev" />。玩家能在游戏开始前选择天气<ref name="gsrev">{{cite web | last = Lopez | first = Tony | title = ''Flight Unlimited III'' | publisher = [[GameSpot|GameSpot]] | date = 1999-09-10 | access-date = 2001-02-08 | url = http://www.zdnet.com/gamespot/stories/reviews/0,10867,2536064,00.html | archivedate = 2001-02-08 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20010208002918/http://www.zdnet.com/gamespot/stories/reviews/0,10867,2536064,00.html | dead-url = yes}}</ref>，[[冷锋|冷锋]]、雷暴等天气实时生成<ref name="pcgameruk">{{cite web | last = Evans | first = Dean | title = Poetic | date = 1999-12 | archivedate = 2002-06-27 | access-date = 2002-06-27 | dead-url = yes | url = http://www.pcgamer.co.uk/games/gamefile_review_page.asp?item_id=2450 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20020627053005/http://www.pcgamer.co.uk/games/gamefile_review_page.asp?item_id=2450 | work = [[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer UK]]}}</ref>。

游戏默认采用“快速飞行”模式，玩家还能选择教程或“挑战”任务。教程模式共有26节<ref name="cgwrev" />，演示基本和高级飞行技巧并由玩家试验操作<ref name="ign" />。挑战任务检验玩家的驾驶功底，任务目标如寻找[[大腳怪|大腳怪]]、营救遇困游客、阻止盗窃案，以及从大圈中间飞过<ref name="ign" /><ref name="pczone">{{cite web | last = Bradley | first = Simon | title = ''Flight Unlimited III'' | work = PC Zone | access-date = 2021-01-01 | url = https://archive.org/stream/PC_Zone_Issue_082_1999-11_Dennis_Publishing_GB#page/n85/mode/2up | date = 1999-11}}</ref>。游戏默认共有11个挑战任务，玩家还能自行制作或从网上下载任务<ref name="manual" />。《无限飞行III》包含开发游戏使用的[[關卡_(電子遊戲)|关卡编辑器]]<ref name="flightsim1">{{cite web | last = Linton | first = Dan | title = Visiting Looking Glass Studios | access-date = 2007-04-08 | dead-url = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070408162238/http://www.flightsim.com/cgi/kds?%24=main%2Froadtrips%2Flglass.htm | url = http://www.flightsim.com/cgi/kds?$=main/roadtrips/lglass.htm | publisher = Flightsim.com | year = 1999 | archivedate = 2007-04-08 }}</ref>，玩家可利用游戏[[三维模型|模型]]设计机场、人工智能飞行路线，还能编辑风景。此外，玩家还能在网上分享创作成果。<ref name="gsrev" />

== 开发 ==
1997年《无限飞行II》面世后，部分开发组成员希望继续研发《无限飞行III》，但也有人想制作[[空战模拟游戏|空战模拟游戏]]《[[简氏攻击中队|飞行战斗]]》（''{{lang|en|Flight Combat}}''）。[[望远镜工作室|望远镜工作室]]（{{lang|en|Looking Glass Studios}}）决定同时开发两个游戏，原有团队分为两组并招新人协助。公司接下来向消费者抽样调查，确定《无限飞行III》的地点等内容。<ref name="ocampo">{{cite web | last = Ocampo | first = Jason | title = Input wanted on Looking Glass sims | url = http://www.cdmag.com/articles/010/085/looking_glass_survey.html | date = 1998-02-16 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20050502210813/http://www.cdmag.com/articles/010/085/looking_glass_survey.html | archivedate = 2005-05-02 | work = Computer Games Magazine}}</ref><ref name="survey">{{cite web | year = 1998 | url = http://www.lglass.com/survey/index.html | publisher = Looking Glass Studios | access-date = 1999-10-12 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/19991012012709/http://www.lglass.com/survey/index.html | title = What's up in the Looking Glass Flying Circus? | archivedate = 1999-10-12}}</ref>1998年5月，[[艺电|艺电]]确认负责《无限飞行III》、《[[网络奇兵2|网络奇兵2]]》（''{{lang|en|System Shock 2}}''）等游戏和推广的销售<ref name="businesswire">{{cite news | title = Electronic Arts and Looking Glass Studios Form Co-Publishing Partnership; ''System Shock 2'' and ''Flight Unlimited III'' Are First Games in Multi-Title Agreement | date = 1998-05-29 | newspaper = [[美國商業資訊|Business Wire]]}}</ref>。望远镜工作室希望以《无限飞行II》为基础打造续作，项目负责人汤姆·斯佩里（{{lang|en|Tom Sperry}}）自称要为玩家提供“最真实环境中飞行的愉悦和感觉”<ref name="survey" /><ref name="combatsim">{{cite web | last = Hjalmarson | first = Leonard | date = 1999-02-16 | title = ''Flight Unlimited III'' Interview | url = http://www.combatsim.com/htm/feb99/fu3-pre1.htm | publisher = combatsim | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180208124436/http://www.combatsim.com/htm/feb99/fu3-pre1.htm | dead-url = yes | archivedate = 2018-02-08 | access-date = 2021-01-01}}</ref>。1998年8月，望远镜工作室在“{{lang|en|MicroWINGS}}”大会上首度展示《无限飞行III》，并宣布根据玩家要求将游戏中的主场定在西雅图及周边，[[普吉特海湾|普吉特海湾]]多变的天气和地形也是选择这里的重要原因<ref name="manual" /><ref name="cdmag2" />。工作室还表示，游戏中很可能增加新机型，地面有活动物体，还打算加入实时并符合物理特征的天气系统<ref name="cdmag2">{{cite web | last = Ocampo | first = Jason | date = 1998-08-21 | title = ''Flight Unlimited III'' Unveiled | url = http://www.cdmag.com/articles/013/193/flight_unlimited_3_details.html | access-date = 2005-04-07 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20050407233307/http://www.cdmag.com/articles/013/193/flight_unlimited_3_details.html | archivedate = 2005-04-07 | work = Computer Games Magazine | dead-url = yes}}</ref><ref name="pressrelease">{{cite press release | title = Looking Glass Reveals First Information About ''Flight Unlimited III'' at MicroWINGS Flight Simulation Conference | date = 1998-08-21 | publisher = Looking Glass Studios | location = Orlando, Florida | url = http://www.lglass.com/c_info/fu3.html | archivedate = 2000-06-11 | access-date = 2000-06-11 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20000611064726/http://www.lglass.com/c_info/fu3.html | dead-url = yes}}</ref>。

曾参与创作《无限飞行II》的前[[飞行教练|飞行教练]]彼得·詹姆斯（{{lang|en|Peter James}}）担任新续作主设计师，主要负责《无限飞行III》的教程、飞机和模拟飛行儀表。詹姆斯认为，其他飞行模拟器在真实程度上尚有欠缺，希望给予玩家更准确的体验。<ref name="flightsim1" />开发组拍摄各种飞机的真实照片，前[[莎草纸设计集团|莎草纸设计集团]]（{{lang|en|Papyrus Design Group}}）汽车建模师邓肯·徐（{{lang|en|Duncan Hsu}}）带队创作飞机三维模型<ref name="manual" /><ref name="flightsim1" />。凯文·瓦瑟曼（{{lang|en|Kevin Wasserman}}）编码飞行物理系统，其中涉及实时[[向量|力学向量]]计算，例如飞机偏航、俯仰和横滚时的力学向量<ref name="flightsim1" />。《无限飞行II》也有力学向量计算系统<ref name="gamespot">{{cite web | access-date = 2021-01-01 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20201118043833/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/flight-unlimited-ii-preview/1100-2558717/ | url = https://www.gamespot.com/articles/flight-unlimited-ii-preview/1100-2558717/ | title = ''Flight Unlimited II'' Preview | last = MacDonald | first = T. Liam | date = 2004-02-27 | archivedate = 2020-11-18 | publisher = [[GameSpot|GameSpot]] | dead-url = no}}</ref>，但不及新作先进<ref name="combatsim" />。飞行物理编码以“真实飞机数据”和飞行员亲身体验为依据，游戏中涉及的每种飞机都经过试飞获取研究资料<ref name="manual" />。飞行员批评过去《无限飞行》系统游戏的座舱太虚假，开发组吸取教训，力争让新作座舱尽量真实<ref name="ign1" />。凯末尔·阿马拉辛汉姆（{{lang|en|Kemal Amarasingham}}）录制各机型的音效，自称曾“冒生命危险”站在喷气发动机和机翼附近<ref name="flightsim1" />。
[[File:Space_Needle002.jpg|thumb]]入选《无限飞行III》主场的重要原因是这里天气和景观多变]]

游戏的地形[[材质贴图|材质贴图]]是用[[卫星影像|卫星影像]]渲染，每像素代表四平方米<ref name="cgw1">{{cite journal | last = Atkin | first = Denny | title = ''Flight Unlimited III''; Night Skies and Stormy Weather Over Seattle | date = 1999-05 | issue = 178 | journal = Computer Gaming World | pages = 78–79}}</ref>，创下飞行模拟器最高分辨率的新纪录<ref name="ign1">{{cite web | last = Blevins | title = ''Flight Unlimited III'' | access-date = 2008-03-18 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080318170925/http://pc.ign.com/articles/130/130979p1.html | date = 1999-05-13 | url = http://pc.ign.com/articles/130/130979p1.html | publisher = IGN | archivedate = 2008-03-18 | first = Tal | dead-url = yes}}</ref>。凯伦·沃尔夫（{{lang|en|Karen Wolff}}）将大型地形图拼接组合，重建西雅图地区地形<ref name="flightsim1" />，在由此形成的多边形网格上覆盖卫星图层<ref name="cgw1" />。除西雅图地区外，游戏还包含八个美国西部州的地形，同样采用真实海拔数据但分辨率不及主场。玩家希望游戏包含全美地形，但受预算和[[CD-ROM|CD-ROM]]格式[[電腦數據存貯器|容量]]限制无法实现。<ref name="manual" />地面移动的三维物体是卓佑善（{{lang|en|Yoosun Cho}}）设计，从摄影书籍获取创作灵感。她利用游戏的对象编辑器，令物体沿路线来回移动或循环往复<ref name="flightsim1" />。詹姆斯等人共同设计天气系统<ref name="flightsim1" />，计算[[湿度|湿度]]、[[山岳推力|山岳推力]]等实体大气数据来生成、移动和扩散[[鋒_(氣象)|锋]]<ref name="ign1" />。

=== 管理和发行前几个月 ===
为报导《无限飞行III》开发过程，新闻工作者丹·林顿（{{lang|en|Dan Linton}}）造访望远镜工作室，对斯佩里、制作人桑德拉·史密斯（{{lang|en|Sandra Smith}}）、营销副总裁迈克尔·马里佐拉（{{lang|en|Michael Malizola}}）的团队管理手法颇感佩服。林顿的报导声称，面对团队，斯佩里等人总是“建议和鼓励”，而非“发号施令”，在他看来，这正是《无限飞行III》“树立业界新标准”的重要原因。<ref name="flightsim1" />詹姆斯事后表示，望远镜工作室当时最畅销的作品是《[[神偷：暗黑计划|神偷：暗黑计划]]》这类动作导向游戏，所以《无限飞行III》开发期间公司管理层整体态度冷淡。他还称，开发组本来非常积极乐观，但管理层的态度导致他们“情绪低落，有时甚至感到愤怒”。詹姆斯、史密斯和斯佩里曾向公司高管呈请制订计划，增设附加组件及第三方开发，但詹姆斯认为公司根本没有理睬。他利用闲暇时间设计续作构想，但公司决定除非《无限飞行III》销量超过《[[微軟模擬飛行系列|微软模拟飞行2000]]》才会开发《无限飞行IV》，落实詹姆斯的构想。詹姆斯觉得艺电对《无限飞行III》的市场宣传不力，公司的要求根本不切实际。他还称，《无限飞行III》空有了不起的销售计划，但束手束脚之下根本无从发挥。<ref name="james1">{{cite web | last = James | first = Peter | title = Behind The Looking Glass | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20060620212538/http://www.flightsim.com/cgi/kds?%24=main%2Fspecial%2Flglass.htm | url = http://www.flightsim.com/cgi/kds?$=main/special/lglass.htm | archivedate = 2006-06-20 | year = 2000 | publisher = Flightsim.com | dead-url = yes | access-date = 2006-06-20 }}</ref>

游戏官方网站在1999年3月开放<ref name="cgm3">{{cite web | last = Fudge | first = James | date = 1999-03-25 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20050502204704/http://www.cdmag.com/articles/018/146/fu3_website.html | title = ''Flight Unlimited III'' Website Opens | archivedate = 2005-05-02 | access-date = 2005-05-02 | dead-url = yes | url = http://www.cdmag.com/articles/018/146/fu3_website.html | work = Computer Games Magazine}}</ref>。同年五月，《无限飞行III》与《飞行战斗：欧洲雷霆》（{{lang|en|Flight Combat: Thunder Over Europe}}）在[[E3电子娱乐展|E3电子娱乐展]]展出<ref name="flightsim2">{{cite press release | title = Looking Glass Studios Announces E3 Line-up | url = http://www.flightsim.com/cgi/kds?$=main/blt/glasse3.htm | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20040829195345/http://www.flightsim.com/cgi/kds?%24=main%2Fblt%2Fglasse3.htm | location = Cambridge, Massachusetts | publisher = Looking Glass Studios | date = 1999-05-13 | archivedate = 2004-08-29 | dead-url = yes | access-date = 2004-08-29 }}</ref>。[[IGN|IGN]]刊登塔尔·布列文（{{lang|en|Tal Blevins}}）的文章，自称年初就看到游戏进入实时天气系统的最后开发阶段，如今可谓千呼万唤始出来<ref name="ign1" />。《全力》杂志称赞游戏中的云层质感出众，抬头显示器画面流畅<ref name="ftmag">{{cite web | title = A Look At Some of the Faces Behind Flight Simulation | date = 1999-05 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20000621143124/http://www.ftmagazine.com/e3.htm | url = http://www.ftmagazine.com/e3.htm | archivedate = 2000-06-21 | work = Full Throttle | access-date = 2000-06-21}}</ref>。“MicroWINGS”称赞游戏采用的16位增强色和高分辨率地形贴图<ref name="microwings">{{cite web | year = 1999 | title = EA/Looking Glass's ''Flight Unlimited III'' shown at E3 | access-date = 2001-01-19 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20010119141500/http://www.microwings.com/pressreleases/pre399c.html | url = http://www.microwings.com/pressreleases/pre399c.html | work=MicroWINGS | archivedate = 2001-01-19}}</ref>。1999年7月，《无限飞行III》又在[[奥什科什航空展览会|奥什科什航空展览会]]展出<ref name="oshkosh">{{cite web | title = ''Flight Unlimited III'' at Oshkosh! | url = http://www.flightsim.com/cgi/kds?$=main/blt/fu3-osh.htm | date = 1999-07-30 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20041025145507/http://www.flightsim.com/cgi/kds?%24=main%2Fblt%2Ffu3-osh.htm | publisher = Flightsim.com | archivedate = 2004-10-25 | dead-url = yes | access-date = 2004-10-25 }}</ref>，詹姆斯称此时游戏已经“完成90%”，[[软件测试|版本测试]]即将结束，还称公众反响热烈，团队得到短时间的激励<ref name="james1" />。《无限飞行III》八月推出[[軟件版本週期|完成版]]<ref name="gold">{{cite web | last = Fudge | first = James | title = ''Flight Unlimited II'' Goes Gold | url = http://www.cdmag.com/articles/022/061/fu3.html | dead-url = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20050515013601/http://www.cdmag.com/articles/022/061/fu3.html | date = 1999-08-20 | archivedate = 2005-05-15 | work = Computer Games Magazine}}</ref>，落后计划九个月。据詹姆斯回忆，开发组举办小型晚宴庆祝，“此后几天大家就在看会有多少人辞职”<ref name="james1" />。詹姆斯本人也在游戏完成后离开望远镜工作室，加入致力飞行模拟器新闻和评论的网站{{lang|en|[[Flightsim.com|Flightsim.com]]}}<ref name="james2">{{cite web | last = James | first = Peter | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080310220133/http://www.flightsim.com/cgi/kds?%24=main%2Fspecial%2Fbj400a.htm | title = Behind The Looking Glass – The BeechJet 400A Revealed | url = http://www.flightsim.com/cgi/kds?$=main/special/bj400a.htm | archivedate = 2008-03-10 | year = 2000 | publisher = Flightsim.com | dead-url = yes | access-date = 2021-12-23 }}</ref>。《无限飞行III》于1999年9月17日发行<ref name="release">{{cite web | last = Fudge | first = James | title = ''Flight Unlimited III'' Released | access-date = 2005-04-06 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20050406140956/http://www.cdmag.com/articles/022/189/fu3_ships.html | url = http://www.cdmag.com/articles/022/189/fu3_ships.html | archivedate = 2005-04-06 | date = 1999-09-17 | work = Computer Games Magazine}}</ref>。

